creator: Joseph. A. Dacus
description:
LibriVox recording of Life and Adventures of Frank and Jesse James by Joseph. A. Dacus.
Read in English by PJ Landau
Biographies of Frank and Jesse James, detailed accounts of all their significant escapades, and the final outcomes. - Summary by PJ Landau
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
